      • migrateNodeAction

        public void migrateNodeAction(com.dpsframework.domain.Migrate mg,
                     jade.lang.acl.ACLMessage propose)
        Serve Migrate Action to Problem-Solvers Ontology. This method generate following special message, build new Monitor2NodeRE-Initiator Behaviour instance and assign that confirmation message to RE-Initiator Behaviour of FIPA-Request Standard Protocol. 
         ----------------
 Example:
 ----------------
 
  (ACCEPT-PROPOSAL
   :sender    ( agent-identifier :name Agent@127.0.0.1:1099/JADE  
                               :addresses (sequence http://PEGASUS:7778/acc ))
   :receiver  (set ( agent-identifier :name Stage@127.0.0.1:1099/JADE  
                               :addresses (sequence http://PEGASUS:7778/acc )) 
                        )
   :content  "((done 
                    (migrate    :app bin 
                                :args CLIPS 
                                :clazz com.dpsframework.util.PsStageNode 
                                :container Container-4 
                                :node Stage)))"
                               
   :reply-with  Stage@127.0.0.1:1099/JADE1492786417822  
   :language  fipa-sl0  
   :ontology  Problem-Solvers  
   :conversation-id  Basal_Migration 
 )
        Parameters:
        mg - Action migrate sent by NodeRequester.
        propose - Message complete received by MonitorAgent.
